  title: Scriptable Objects - Events
  text: '- Scriptable Objects can be used to implement a robust <style="highlight">event
    system</style>

    - We can do so by storing a list of listeners in Scriptable
    Objects

    - Since Scriptable objects are assets, we can eliminate scene references
    in <style="highlight">prefabs</style>

